ixa.kaflib

Class Term

  • java.lang.Object
    • ixa.kaflib.IReferable
      • ixa.kaflib.Term
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TLinkReferable, Serializable, Comparable<IReferable>

    public class Term
extends IReferable
implements Serializable
    Class for representing terms. Terms refer to previous word forms (and groups multi-words) and attach lemma, part of speech, synset and name entity information.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
